menu "FIDO2 / Passkey authenticator"

    config FIDO2_DEBUG_LOG
        bool "Enable verbose FIDO2 diagnostic logging"
        default n
        help
            Log every HID packet receive event, CTAPHID dispatch header, CBOR
            command code, and per-packet stack HWM to the in-memory diagnostic
            buffer (readable from the Passkey tab in the web UI).

            When disabled only command results (#N cmd → STATUS) and errors are
            logged, which is sufficient for normal production use.

endmenu
